          <p>
            CALL FOR REQUEST FOR QUALIFICATIONS TO UNDERTAKE THE DEVELOPMENT
            OF ZAMBIA ARMY PROJECTS THROUGH PUBLIC PRIVATE PARTNERSHIP (PPP)
            ZA/RFQ/PPP/01/2020
          </p>

